{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1695-12_140", "resp": "louise"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Plan de l'amphithéâtre antique redécouvert à Valognes (théâtre d'Alauna)]*"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", décembre 1695 [tome 13], p. 140-144."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/note[1]", "tag": "note", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/note[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/note[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Avis pour placer les Figures"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/note[1]/text()[1]", "text": " : La Figure doit regarder la page 141."}], "attributes": {"resp": "author", "place": "margin"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Je ne vous envoye point le Plan du Fort de Bourbon, que je vous avois promis la derniere fois, parce qu’on le trouvera dans l’Almanach de M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[2]", "text": " Langlois. C’est un Ouvrage, qui, si on luy oste le nom d’Almanach, merite d’estre regardé comme un tres beau morceau d’histoire en Taille-douce, à cause de ses recherches exactes & curieuses. Au lieu de ce Fort, je vous envoye une figure qui doit vous faire plaisir. C’est le Plan de l’Amphitheatre, dont je vous ay déjà parlé, & qui a esté trouvé à Valogne, proche la maison de Franquetot. En voicy l’explication, selon les lettres marquées dans la figure,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "A"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": ". L’Orchestre."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[3]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[3]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[3]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "B"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[3]/text()[1]", "text": ". Premier cercle de muraille qui ferme l’Orchestre."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[4]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[4]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[4]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "C"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[4]/text()[1]", "text": ". Muraille de renfort, où aboutissent les degrez."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[5]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[5]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[5]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "D"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[5]/text()[1]", "text": ". L’ouverture des degrez."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[6]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[6]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[6]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "E"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[6]/text()[1]", "text": ". Grosse muraille au haut des degrez, entre lesquels paroist une muraille marquée "}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[6]/hi[2]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[6]/hi[2]/text()[1]", "text": "F"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[6]/text()[2]", "text": ". qui laisse entre elle & la grosse muraille, un espace à placer sept bancs par étage les uns derriere les autres."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[7]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[7]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[7]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "G"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[7]/text()[1]", "text": ". La grosse muraille formant une demi-ovale."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[8]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[8]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[8]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "H"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[8]/text()[1]", "text": ". Grosse muraille qui coupe l’ovale."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[9]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[9]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[9]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "I"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[9]/text()[1]", "text": ". Murailles avancées au delà de la traversante, où estoit le Pupitre des Anciens, en Latin "}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[9]/hi[2]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[9]/hi[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Pulpitium"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[9]/text()[2]", "text": ", lieu où les Acteurs joüoient, &c."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[10]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[10]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[10]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "K"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[10]/text()[1]", "text": ". Autre Postscenium."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[11]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[11]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[11]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "L"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[11]/text()[1]", "text": ". Grosse muraille servant comme d’arc boutant."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[12]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[12]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[12]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "M"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[12]/text()[1]", "text": ". Muraille au deça de la traversante, pour renforcer & soutenir l’ouvrage."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[13]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[13]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[13]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "N"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[13]/text()[1]", "text": ". Muraille répondant à celle d’en haut marquée "}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[13]/hi[2]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[13]/hi[2]/text()[1]", "text": "F"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[13]/text()[2]", "text": ". laissant un vuide entre elle & l’Orchestre, à mettre sept ou neuf bancs les uns derriere les autres."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[14]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[14]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[14]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "O"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[14]/text()[1]", "text": ". La place des Spectateurs."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[15]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[15]/text()[1]", "text": "Les petits points noirs marquent la place des murailles qui separoient les espaces qui contenoient sept ou neuf bancs. Ils sont appellez les Palliers, & servoient comme de reposoirs de sept en sept marches, & faisoient assez bien la forme de galeries."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[16]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[16]/text()[1]", "text": "Les lignes traînantes & entrecoupées au dessus du Renvoy, sont des fondemens & mines couvertes de ronces & brossailles, d’une grosseur notable, qui bornoit la veuë des Spectateurs."}]}]}